@node "Requirements" "Requirements"
@{fg shine}@{bg fill} Requirements@{fg text}@{bg back}
  You need:
   - an AMIGA :-)
   - a Modem :-))
   - OS 3.x (not tested on OS 2.x-)
   - some free KB of RAM..
@endnode

